<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng xīn zhù fú 迦南1035</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng xīn zhù fú měi wèi xiǎo péng yǒu, yuàn zhǔ yǔ nǐ men tóng zài.
 bù pà cuò zhé hé shī bài, yǒng gǎn miàn duì wèi lái.
 zhǔ shì nǐ suí shí bāng zhù, zhǔ shì nǐ de jiān gù tái. zhǔ shì nǐ shēng mìng de zhǔ zǎi,
 yòu shì nǐ zhì huì zhī shì de yuán tóu. yǒu yí wèn bì gěi nǐ jiě kāi.
 zàn měi zhǔ de jiù ēn, gē chàng shén de cí ài.
 dāng bǎ zhè měi hǎo de shí guāng xiàn gěi zhǔ, xiàng shì jiè jiàn zhèng shén de ài.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1035</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>